*The Hunger Games Is Mocking God* | The Hunger Games is an award-winning film series that has captivated the minds of many. At face value, it may appear to be nothing more than action-packed entertainment, but when you take a closer look, this film series is a biblical re-tellling of the war between God and Satan. Let's explore together how this film series seeks to subliminally dilute and destroy the Word of God.
